{"tid":2227427,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"偽裝獨立媒體 俄網路組織意圖再次操弄美國大選輿論","createTime":"2020-10-02T18:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T02:47:52.000Z","uid":176447,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"41c72db4bafd307276609632d19ae8ff5241f1ac","tid":2227427,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:51:30.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕一個以聖彼得堡為基地的俄國網路研究組織於2016年總統大選就被指控操弄美國輿論，近來又被發現成立了「美洲和歐洲公民新聞室」（Newsroom for American and European Based Citizens，簡稱NAEBC）......<br />\n<br />\n據路透報導，NAEBC表面上是匈牙利自由獨立媒體，主頁還警示：「別讓人給愚弄過去。」聚焦於美國政治、時事，轉貼右翼媒體新聞，以合成人像徵求撰稿者，並聘請真正的美國人撰文探討敏感政治話題，........ 這個俄國網路研究組織也以相似手法成立了左翼媒體頻道「和平資料庫」（Peace Data）。<br />\n<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\nNAEBC自6月活躍至今，........<br />\n<br />\n路透記者聯繫NAEBC，詢問他們與俄國關聯時，一位自稱白卡（Nora Berka）的助理編輯拒絕視訊與電訪，單單以文字回應NAEBC與任何勢力無干。之後，白卡和其他NAEBC職員紛紛從社群網站上刪除了部分貼文，個人資料也抹去了與NAEBC的所有關聯。<br />\n<br />\n克里姆林宮發言人佩斯科夫（Dmitry Peskov）則指稱，俄方對NAEBC與「和平資料庫」毫不知情。美國聯邦調查局對此不予置評。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3309336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309336&d=ooVnpwewILBg1HoWGmAtmVDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=1c042daf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3309336&h=a1157006\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3309336</a>"},{"pid":"6e4f6903ab72ed315e357bdc08357f10913cc882","tid":2227427,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T18:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tenoc1N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTenoc1N.png&h=389af7d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00ed5811a1dac1f963dc92d0c19c3a4575433a47","tid":2227427,"uid":70313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-02T19:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5731a7c407c70c53513803c5ef20c12625468fc8","tid":2227427,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"操弄美國大選，都係幫侵侵姐。"}]}